data.text:
2022 (R-Sophomore): Named to the SoCon Honor Roll ... Played in all 11 games, primarily on special team ... Made his ETSU debut in the season opening win over Mars Hill where he had one tackle ... Recorded another tackle at Mercer.

2021 (R-Freshman): Did not appear in any games in his first year with ETSU.

Previous School(s)

Bluefield College

2020 (Freshman): Appeared and started in all nine games for Bluefield College as a true freshman … Had an 18-tackle performance against Kentucky Christian.

High School: Lettered in football … Was named First Team All-District and First Team All-Region as a senior in high school … Finished the senior season with 125 tackles.
